      <h2>1. Not Financial Advice</h2>

      <p>All content on DogeKing.us is published for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. Nothing on this website constitutes financial advice, investment advice, trading advice, or any other form of professional advice. You should not treat any of the Site's content as a recommendation to buy, sell, or hold any cryptocurrency or other investment.</p>



      <p>Cryptocurrency investments are <strong>highly speculative and volatile</strong>. Prices can go to zero. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Always conduct your own independent research and consult with a qualified financial advisor before making any investment decisions.</p>



      <h2>2. No Guarantees</h2>

      <p>DogeKing makes no guarantees regarding:</p>

      <ul>

        <li>The accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of any information on the Site</li>

        <li>The future price, value, or performance of $DKING or any other cryptocurrency</li>

        <li>The success or viability of any project mentioned on the Site</li>

        <li>Any investment returns or outcomes</li>

      </ul>



      <h2>3. $DKING Token</h2>

      <p>$DKING is a <strong>meme coin</strong> on the Solana blockchain. It has no guaranteed utility, intrinsic value, or promise of returns. Like all meme coins and cryptocurrencies, $DKING carries significant risks including:</p>

      <ul>

        <li>Total loss of value</li>

        <li>Market manipulation</li>

        <li>Liquidity issues</li>

        <li>Regulatory uncertainty</li>

        <li>Smart contract vulnerabilities</li>

      </ul>



      <h2>4. Do Your Own Research (DYOR)</h2>

      <p>We strongly encourage you to perform your own due diligence before investing in any cryptocurrency. This includes:</p>

      <ul>

        <li>Reading the project's whitepaper and documentation</li>

        <li>Verifying the team's background and credentials</li>

        <li>Checking tokenomics, supply distribution, and lock-up periods</li>

        <li>Reviewing smart contract audits (if available)</li>

        <li>Assessing market liquidity and trading volume</li>

        <li>Understanding the risks unique to meme coin investments</li>

      </ul>



      <h2>5. Forward-Looking Statements</h2>

      <p>From time to time, the Site may contain forward-looking statements regarding DogeKing's roadmap, development plans, or potential future outcomes. These statements are based on current expectations and involve known and unknown risks. Actual results may differ materially.</p>



      <h2>6. Investment Risk Warning</h2>

      <div class="warning-box">

        <p><strong>âÅ¡ ïÂ¸Â RISK WARNING:</strong> Cryptocurrency trading and investing carries extreme risk. You could lose all of your invested capital. Never invest money you cannot afford to lose. Meme coins are among the most volatile and risky assets in the cryptocurrency space. Prices can experience rapid and substantial fluctuations within very short timeframes.</p>

      </div>



      <h2>7. Third-Party Content & Links</h2>

      <p>Our Site may reference or link to third-party projects, exchanges, platforms, or individuals. These references are for informational purposes only and do not constitute endorsements. We are not responsible for the actions, content, or practices of any third party.</p>



      <h2>8. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>

      <p>Some links on DogeKing.us may be affiliate links. If you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you. We only recommend products and services that we believe provide value to our readers. You are under no obligation to use our affiliate links.</p>



      <h2>9. No Fiduciary Relationship</h2>

      <p>Use of DogeKing.us does not create any fiduciary relationship between you and DogeKing or any of its team members. We are not your financial advisor, broker, or fiduciary. All decisions based on information from this Site are your sole responsibility.</p>



      <h2>10. Contact</h2>

      <p>If you have questions about this disclaimer, please contact us at <strong>DogeKing.us@gmail.com</strong>.</p>



